# 🍪 Crumbling Cookies
### *A Card Game of Fate, Frogs, and Forbidden Baked Goods*

**2–3 Players · Ages 10+ · 15–30 min**

---

> *A cursed batch of cookies has been baked. Somewhere in the cookie jar lurks a **Crumbling Cookie** — and if you draw one, you're out... unless you have a Milk Splash to save yourself. Use spells, frogs, vinyl records and sheer dice-rolling luck to outlast everyone else.*

---

