## 🎮 Setup

1. Remove all **Crumbling Cookies** and **Milk Splashes** from the deck.
2. Deal **4 cards** to each player. Then deal **1 Milk Splash** to each player *(5 cards total per player)*.
3. Shuffle the Crumbling Cookies back in — **one fewer than the number of players**.
   - 2 players → 1 cookie · 3 players → 2 cookies
   - You may have leftover Milk Splashes — shuffle up to **3 extras** back into the deck.
4. Shuffle the deck.
5. **Sweetest player (Whoever most recently ate something sweet) goes first.**

Disclaimer: Biting Sugar must be done with consent

---

## 🔄 On Your Turn

1. *(Optional)* Play any number of action cards from your hand.
2. Your turn ends when you or another player **Draws a card** from the deck or a **card effect ends your turn** earlier. 

> ⚠️ **Drew a Crumbling Cookie?**
> Play a **Milk Splash** to survive — then secretly reinsert the cookie anywhere in the deck. No Milk Splash? Your **cookie crumbles** (you're elimated).
> If an action causes another player to draw card(s), your turn ends and it is now the attacked players turn.
> Keep Milk Splashes in a separate discard pile, slightly spread out so players can count how many are there.

---

## 🏆 Winning

The **last intact cookie** wins the cookie jar. Glory, crumbs, and bragging rights are yours.

---

## 🃏 Card Reference

---

### 🐸 Leaping Frog — Defense
**Skip your draw phase.** Pass the turn to the next player — no draw, no risk.

If drawing multiple cards by another action's effect, each Leaping Frog skips **one** of those draws. 

*"Ribbit. Not today."*

---

### 🛡️ Shield Spell — Defense / Reaction
**Play as a reaction when any card is played** — including another Shield Spell. Cancel its effect entirely. Must be played within 7 seconds of an action target being chosen.

- Can be played **outside your turn** to defend against another players' shenanigans.
- Two Shield Spells cancel **each other**.

*"Spell slot: used."*

---

### 🥣 Stir the Batter — Deck / Utility
**Shuffle the entire draw pile (no peeking).** 

*"The prophecy has been... amended."*

---

### 🔮 Crystal Crumb — Info / Deck
Look at the **top 3 cards** of the deck and **replace them in any order.**

*"It's giving… oracle energy."*

---

### 🎵 Vinyl Scratch — Disruption
**Reverse the turn order.** 
End your turn(s) immediately without drawing a card.
Play continues in the new direction until another Vinyl Scratch is played.

*"B-side activated."*

---

### 🎲 Roll 4 Initiative — Dice
Roll the die and consult the result:

| Roll | Effect |
|------|--------|
| 1–3 | Skip your draw phase entirely |
| 4 | Draw up to 3 cards yourself *(or fewer if the deck has less than 3)* |
| 5–6 | Force any one player to draw up to 2 cards *(or fewer if the deck has less than 2)*|
This ends your turn(s) and play continues with the person following the person drawing.

*"Nat 4 goes hard actually."*

---

### 💀 Cursed Die — Dice / Attack
**Play on any other player.** They must roll the die:

| Roll | Effect |
|------|--------|
| 1–2 | They discard 1 card of their choice |
| 3–4 | They discard 2 cards of their choice |
| 5–6 | They discard 3 cards of their choice |

*"The cookie crumbles… for thee."*

---

### 🍪 Cookies Accepted — Info
**Choose any player.** Peek at **3 random cards** from their hand *(or their full hand if they have fewer than 3)*.

*"Privacy settings: off."*

---

### 📜 Extra Serving — Draw
**Draw 2 cards** from the top of the deck. This ends your turn. You cannot play action cards in between the draws.

*"Seconds? Don't mind if I do."*

---

### 🥛 Stolen Sip — Attack
**Point to a specific card not in the discard pile** *(by position, not by name)*. If it's a **Milk Splash**, take it into your hand. If it's anything else, nothing happens.

- Can be a card at the top of the draw pile or an opponents hand.


*"Oops. Their safety net: gone."*

---

### 📖 Mimicry Scroll — Wildcard
**Discard an additional card to copy the effect of any card in the discard pile.** You may not copy Crumbling Cookie or Milk Splash.

*"I'm not plagiarizing. I'm paying homage."*

